Title: Establishes the distinctive "Women Veterans" license plates and the women veterans support fund
Summary: Relates to establishing distinctive "Women Veterans" license plates and the women veterans support fund; establishes that moneys of the fund will be used for women veterans homelessness, counseling and other programs that support women veterans.
